title: Party Starters
overview: In the premiere of Party Starters, Simon Iversen, Mariyah Samia, Albert Dyrlund and Anne Plejdrup fight to hold the best and wildest party. The four take turns inviting each other to a party, and it does not go quietly! They do everything to impress their guests with their abilities as Party Starters with wild and cross-border surprises. After each party, guests must give points to the program's Party Starter. And in the last section, they finally find out who is Denmark's best Party Starter!
